---

<section id="features" class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
    <p class="text-cyan-600 font-semibold text-center mb-2">Features</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">有料ツールに負けない、充実の機能</h2>
    <p class="section-subtitle">LINE公式アカウントの運用に必要な機能をすべて搭載。独自開発だから、カスタマイズも自由自在。</p>

    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
      {features.map((feature) => (
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-gray-100 hover:border-cyan-200 hover:shadow-md transition-all group">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-cyan-50 text-cyan-600 flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:bg-cyan-500 group-hover:text-white transition-colors" set:html={feature.icon} />
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-2">{feature.title}</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">{feature.description}</p>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
